=== audit_logs schema ===
                               Tabla «public.audit_logs»
    Columna    |           Tipo           | Ordenamiento | Nulable  |    Por omisión    
---------------+--------------------------+--------------+----------+-------------------
 id            | uuid                     |              | not null | gen_random_uuid()
 actor_user_id | uuid                     |              |          | 
 action        | text                     |              | not null | 
 entity_type   | text                     |              |          | 
 entity_id     | uuid                     |              |          | 
 metadata      | jsonb                    |              | not null | '{}'::jsonb
 created_at    | timestamp with time zone |              | not null | now()
Índices:
    "pk_audit_logs" PRIMARY KEY, btree (id)
    "audit_logs_actor_created_idx" btree (actor_user_id, created_at)
    "audit_logs_created_at_idx" btree (created_at)
    "audit_logs_entity_idx" btree (entity_type, entity_id)
Restricciones de llave foránea:
    "audit_logs_actor_user_id_fkey" FOREIGN KEY (actor_user_id) REFERENCES users(id) ON DELETE SET NULL

